    "#Prompt 4 \"This is a discharge summary for a patient.",
    "Please act as a healthcare professional and provide a response based on the summary using the following instructions: 1.",
    "Identify if a patient has metastatic cancer or not. 2.",
    "If there is clear evidence of metastatic cancer, respond 'Yes'. 3.",
    "If there is no strong evidence of metastatic cancer or if the evidence is unclear, respond 'No.'"
